General.Name: Nilsson Special Vehicles publ AB
General.Description: Nilsson Special Vehicles AB (publ) produces and sells ambulances, limousines, hearses, and other vehicles. The company offers used cars; and ceremonial and transport vehicles for hire. It operates in Europe and Scandinavia. Nilsson Special Vehicles AB (publ) was founded in 1945 and is headquartered in Laholm, Sweden.
